Malosi spells really are up to intuition like Goladus says.  They're too dependant on the mob.  Some exp mobs, doesn't matter at all.  On big mobs, malosini is a must to get slow on, sometimes.  Other times, like Dozekar, the mob's MR is so low that slow is landed before malosini is.  Its not as easy to quantify as a pure damage spell.<br>
<br>
